<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-01-24T12:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-01-24T12:00:00-05:00" n="894" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d894">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 EAC/3–2445: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi>
                                (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Harriman</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-01-24T13:00:00-04:00">24 March
                                    1945—1 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>698. From the Secretary. In response to a question from Ambassador Winant
                            I have informed him that the Department would strive to assure effective
                            coordination between his negotiations in EAC and the work of other
                            Allied authorities and special missions by keeping him fully informed
                            concerning the scope and progress of negotiations elsewhere, and by
                            assuring conformity of other policy discussions with policies developed
                            in EAC. I request that you keep this matter in mind, particularly with
                            respect to the forthcoming deliberations of the Reparation Commission.
                            [Stettinius.]</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>